short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects the default google videos tab to search youtube, instead of the default google videos search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When browsing google, it is sometimes more convenient to have the "videos" tab to redirect straight to youtube. This extension aims to solve this by redirecting the videos tab straight to youtube.
